snippet.title: Hello Bendy [Hello Neighbor x Bendy and the Ink Machine Crossover]
snippet.description:
Introducing Hello Bendy, a Bendy and the Ink Machine Halloween Crossover Mod! Available now as the default build for everyone who Pre-Purchases Hello Neighbor on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/521890/Hello_Neighbor/

Get BATIM: http://store.steampowered.com/app/622650/Bendy_and_the_Ink_Machine/
